_sText:
This map is AWSOME. A few new textures. 'Pakrat'd them into the .bsp file so there should be no problems.

This map can hold up to 60 people, but 20 people runs good to.

FPS are a bit better in most places. 
Bomb no longer falls through the floor if the carrier gets killed around bomb site B.


Thanks to everyone at www.whendarknessfalls.org for play testing
